---
// HighConversionFeatures.astro
---

<section id="ferramentas-conversao" class="py-24 text-brand-dark overflow-hidden relative bg-white">
  <!-- Sunny Yellow Glow Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-60" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, #FFF991 0%, transparent 70%); mix-blend-mode: multiply;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Cabeçalho da Seção -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter text-brand-dark">
        FERRAMENTAS PARA <span class="text-brand-yellow">ALTA CONVERSÃO</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        O arsenal completo para quem não aceita nada menos que o topo do Google.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Seção: RATOEIRA ADS -->
    <div class="mb-32">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="h-px bg-brand-yellow/30 grow"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-yellow font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs px-4 py-2 border border-brand-yellow/30 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow/5">Ratoeira Ads</span>
        <div class="h-px bg-brand-yellow/30 grow"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 auto-rows-fr">
        <!-- Feature Ads 1 -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors italic uppercase leading-none">
              A MORTE<br>DOS BOTS
            </h3>
            <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
              Nossa I.A. detecta e bloqueia cliques fraudulentos e concorrentes mal intencionados em milissegundos. Proteja seu orçamento e pague apenas por humanos reais.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-auto transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <img 
              src="https://ratoeiraadsoficial.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/BLOQUEIO-DE-RATOS-E-BOTS.webp" 
              alt="Blindagem Anti-Fraude" 
              class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-all"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-brand-yellow/5 rounded-full blur-[60px] group-hover:bg-brand-yellow/10 transition-all"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Ads 2 -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors italic uppercase leading-none">
              VISÃO DE<br>PREDADOR
            </h3>
            <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
              Identificamos a origem exata de cada venda — até as que o Google oculta. Saiba qual campanha, anúncio e palavra-chave estão realmente botando dinheiro no seu bolso.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-auto transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <img 
              src="https://ratoeiraadsoficial.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/tracking-de-conversoes-de-verdade.webp" 
              alt="Tracking de Precisão" 
              class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-all"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-brand-yellow/5 rounded-full blur-[60px] group-hover:bg-brand-yellow/10 transition-all"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature Ads 3 (Full Width) -->
      <div class="mt-8 card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1 relative z-10">
          <span class="text-brand-yellow text-xs font-black uppercase mb-4 block tracking-widest">Controle Total</span>
          <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors italic uppercase leading-tight">
            SEU CENTRO<br>DE COMANDO
          </h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Esqueça 4 abas abertas. ROI, CPA e Lucro Líquido em tempo real. Tome decisões de escala baseadas em lucro real, não em métricas de vaidade do Google.
          </p>
          <a href="#planos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-dark text-white font-black px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-brand-yellow hover:text-brand-dark transition-all group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,184,0,0.3)]">
            Explorar Dashboard
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M14 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="https://ratoeiraadsoficial.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/UM-DASHBOARD-INCRIVEL.webp" 
            alt="Dashboard ROI" 
            class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-black/5"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Seção: RATOEIRA PAGES -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="h-px bg-orange-600/20 grow"></div>
        <span class="text-orange-600 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs px-4 py-2 border border-orange-600/20 rounded-full bg-orange-600/5">Ratoeira Pages</span>
        <div class="h-px bg-orange-600/20 grow"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 auto-rows-fr">
        
        <!-- Feature Pages 1: Flash Pages (Destaque com Imagem) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">FLASH PAGES</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Criação e Validação em Tempo Recorde. Coloque sua oferta no ar enquanto seus concorrentes ainda estão configurando o servidor.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/flash-pages.png" alt="Interface Flash Pages" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Pages 2: Templates Prontos (Layout Invertido) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">TEMPLATES PRONTOS</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Design Profissional ao Seu Alcance. Estruturas validadas por especialistas para garantir que sua página converta desde o primeiro clique.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/templates-prontos.png" alt="Interface Templates Prontos" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Pages 3: Construtor Drag-and-Drop (Destaque com Imagem) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 11.5V14m0-2.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 113 0m-3 6a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v2a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0v-5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-6-3V11m0-5.5v-1a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v1m0 0V11m0-5.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v3m0 0V11"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">CONSTRUTOR DRAG-AND-DROP</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Liberdade Total de Edição. Arraste e solte elementos para criar layouts personalizados sem precisar tocar em uma única linha de código. A ferramenta definitiva para transformar ideias em páginas.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/drag-and-drop.png" alt="Interface Construtor Drag-and-Drop" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Pages 4: Clonador de Páginas (Destaque com Imagem) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">CLONADOR DE PÁGINAS</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Sua Estrutura Própria em Segundos. Importe qualquer página externa para o seu domínio com um único clique e tenha total controle. Economize horas de design e foque apenas no que vende.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/clonador.png" alt="Interface Clonador de Páginas" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Pages 5: Presell Review com IA (Destaque com Imagem - Invertido para Z-Pattern) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0012 18.75c-1.03 0-1.9-.4-2.593-.912l-.547-.547z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">PRESELL REVIEW COM IA</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Análise Inteligente de Oferta. Receba sugestões instantâneas para maximizar o desejo de compra e evitar erros graves de conversão. Sua página revisada por quem entende de escala.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/review-ia.png" alt="Interface Review com IA" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature Pages 6: Integração Ratoeira Ads (Destaque com Imagem) -->
        <div class="card-feature group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 hover:border-orange-600/40 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-orange-600/20 group-hover:bg-orange-600/20 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase text-brand-dark group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-tight">INTEGRAÇÃO RATOEIRA ADS</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Conecte sua página ao Ratoeira Ads nativamente para uma blindagem e tracking infalíveis. A simbiose perfeita entre tráfego e destino. Sua estrutura blindada contra qualquer imprevisto e 100% otimizada para lucro.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
              <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-black/10 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 bg-brand-dark/5">
                <img src="/images/features/integracao.png" alt="Interface Integrações Ratoeira Ads" class="w-full h-auto block" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Final Unificado -->
    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <a href="#planos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-linear-to-r from-brand-yellow to-orange-600 text-brand-dark font-black text-sm md:text-xl py-6 px-8 md:px-12 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_10px_50px_rgba(255,184,0,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_80px_rgba(255,184,0,0.4)] hover:-translate-y-2 group whitespace-nowrap">
        QUERO O ARSENAL COMPLETO
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 transform transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-brand-text/40 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Oferta de aniversário expira em breve</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";

  .card-feature {
    @apply transition-all duration-500;
  }
  .card-feature:hover {
    @apply -translate-y-2;
  }
</style>
